    => deleting duplicates row-by-row is difficult if table contains  huge 
         number of duplicate rows , so execute the following query to delete 
         all duplicate rows from table.

         DELETE
         FROM emp44 a
         WHERE rowid <>  (SELECT MIN(rowid)
                                        FROM emp44
                                        WHERE empno = a.empno
                                                       AND
                                                       ename = a.ename
                                                       AND
                                                       sal = a.sal);
